description: Main Results Table: Enrichment of Gene Sets in Breast Cancer Cell Lines
footnotes: This table shows the enrichment of the breast cancer stem-like cell (CSLC) signature in various breast cancer cell lines. The enrichment score (NES) and p-value indicate the similarity of the cell line's protein activity profile to the CSLC signature. A higher NES indicates a closer resemblance to the CSLC phenotype.
